verbose_text: Saturated fatty acid (SFA) from hypertrophied adipocytes appears to activate toll like receptor (TLR) 4 signaling pathway in adipocytes and macrophages, resulting in the production of proinflammatory cytokine, tumor necrosis factor alpha (TNFalpha).
